title: Tornadoes Touch Down in Northeast Texas
description: Tornadoes tore through parts of Texas, Arkansas and Oklahoma, damaging dozens of homes and leaving thousands of people without power, according to officials.
dc:creator: The Associated Press and Storyful

media:content.media:credit: Jeff Forward/The Paris News, via Associated Press
media:content.media:description: Extensive damage caused by a tornado near Lamar County Road 35940, near Midcity, Texas on Friday.
